AND:
1 & 1  - >  1
--------------
OR :- 
1 | 1  - >  1
--------------
XOR :
1 & 0
0 & 1  ->   1
--------------
~   :
1 -> 0
0 -> 1
--------------
2's ~ :
1's ~ + 1
--------------
leftShit << :
a << b = (a*Pow(2, b))
--------------
rightShift >> :
a >> b = (a/Pow(2, b))
--------------


--------------------------------------
~ formula = -(x+1)